DEMON V1.01 DISTRIBUTION TERMS :
--------------------------------

This is the cut-down, shareware version of Demon. You may use it as
often as you like but are encouraged to support the programmer by
purchasing the full version for a small fee. You will also receive the
full, registered version of Klondike and extra card graphics and sound
effects for both programs.

You are also encouraged to distribute Demon V1.01 to as many Amiga
owners, PD libraries and electronic bulletin boards as possible. I'm not
fortunate enough to own a modem and so will be extremely grateful to
anyone willing to upload this version to a BBS for me.  

Demon V1.01 may be freely distributed as long as the following
conditions are met :


  o No-one may claim copyright to Demon other than the author.
  
  o No other games written by Peter Wiseman may be distributed on
    the same disk as Demon.
  
