The above files and their respective .infos take up around 335K of
disk space.

Additional graphics, sound samples, prefs and hi-scores files may be added
to the Card Faces, Card Symbols, Card Backs, Card Sets, Sound Effects,
Sound Prefs and Scores directories as disk space allows. However, none of
the above files may be deleted or altered to make room for these.

In order for the in-game Print function to work on the doc files, your
system disk should contain a "printer.device" file in the "devs/" drawer,
"Port Handler/" in the "l" drawer and a suitable printer device ("generic"
will do) in the "devs/printers/" drawer. I don't insist that these files
are present on the distribution disk though; only if space allows.


